com.feilong.servlet.http.listener

Class ServletRequestLoggingListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.feilong.servlet.http.listener.ServletRequestLoggingListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, ServletRequestListener

    public class ServletRequestLoggingListener
extends Object
implements ServletRequestListener
    The listener interface for receiving servletRequestLogging events. The class that is interested in processing a servletRequestLogging event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addServletRequestLoggingListener method. When the servletRequestLogging event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
    Since:
    1.10.4
    Author:
    feilong
